content: I've been getting ready for work around 6:30 AM, and lately, I've been making myself a cup of coffee and a slice of toast with avocado for breakfast before heading out the door. I'm thinking that if I switch to bike-sharing, I might need to adjust my morning routine to accommodate the extra time it takes to get to work. Can you tell me more about how to plan my bike commute, including how to estimate the time it takes to bike to work and how to navigate through heavy traffic?
